{"tid":2152942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中資大行傳開始遵守美對港官員制裁措施","createTime":"2020-08-12T09:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T14:53:22.000Z","uid":13663,"like":137,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"503c9c1163da201009a7fe8a9ceb4c4ae948854b","tid":2152942,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"美國財政部早前公布制裁11名中港官員後，外電引述知情人士透露，中國大型國有銀行正採取臨時舉措，以遵守美國對香港官員實施的制裁，進而保障至關重要的美元融資渠道和海外網絡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知情人士表示，在美國擁有業務的中資大行，包括中國銀行(03988)、建設銀行(00939)和招商銀行(03968)對為特首林鄭月娥等11名受制裁官員開設新賬戶態度謹慎，最少一家銀行已暫停了此類活動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知情人士稱，部分銀行禁止了經過美國的交易，原先可以立即處理的一些交易，現在必須經過合規部門的審批。花旗等外資銀行也已採取行動，暫停賬戶或是加強對香港客戶的審查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好嬲好嬲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d49e83f35fbefa8c1673af38a0779d6c7dfdb2","tid":2152942,"uid":13663,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2549833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2549833&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=afb0fddb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2549833</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國快d做野啦"},{"pid":"fd2211a628663ab9d2abba61b9d7d510d4373f5f","tid":2152942,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"鎖國啦"},{"pid":"690518cf144f720a7d63ee603218b4c66d58faf7","tid":2152942,"uid":58209,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:13:38.000Z","msg":"点解要向美国佬跪低？我地中国人既樽盐呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b756aeb128eeaeaa550e4962d1b27ecb27514a","tid":2152942,"uid":129243,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:13:47.000Z","msg